        "message": "=Hi,\n\nWe couldn’t clearly determine whether your last message was an approval or a request for revision.\n\nPlease reply to the latest email with the draft post and images again with:\n\n• \"Approved\" to finalize the post\nOR\n• \"Denied\" and your clean feedback for revisions\n\nThank you!",
